cs.RO, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG

The paper focuses on linking human whole-body motion and natural language, which is relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed approach uses deep recurrent neural networks (RNNs) and sequence-to-sequence learning, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
